summary: Replaces all living trees with giant mushrooms. If that wasn't enough for you, It also replaces every crop in the game with other kinds of mushrooms. Makes nights in skyrim, glow a warm beautiful blue.
descriptionHtml:
Do you enjoy the fine art of mycology? We'll then this is the mod for you!

Replaces all living trees with giant mushrooms. If that wasn't enough for you, It also replaces every crop in the game with other kinds of mushrooms. Makes nights in skyrim, glow a warm beautiful blue. As well as a significant FPS boost at a much more intense beauty. Do NOT use with any mods that modify flora amounts. Retextures should be fine.
author: adrian85858
